OL,9,G1335FA Place in the Sun
OL,10,     GJoe and Fiona love the idyllic
OL,11,     GGreek island of Kefalonia and
OL,12,     Gwant a spacious holiday home
OL,13,     Gwhere they can entertain all the
OL,14,     Gfamily. Can Laura Hamilton find
OL,15,     Gthe one for their #250k?
OL,16,G1440FA Place in the Sun
