OL,4,G1955FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GKeighly and Justin host at The
OL,6,     GHalf Moon Inn, in Norfolk.
OL,7,     GJustin's been talking up his chef
OL,8,     Gcredentials all week. But he
OL,9,     Gshould be wary of the B&Ber's
OL,10,     Gbiggest foe: the poached egg.
OL,11,G2030FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GToilet troubles, tossing and
OL,13,     Gturning, and tears galore. It's a
OL,14,     Grip-roaring payment day on Four
OL,15,     Gin a Bed. But who's won the week?
OL,16,G2100F24 Hours in A&E
OL,17,     GLewis, who's 18, has come off his
OL,18,     Gmotorbike and collided with two
OL,19,     Gcars. Sam, who's 27, fainted and
OL,20,     Gcut his lip while smoking a Cuban
OL,21,     Gcigar at a barbecue.
